folder: Sackett Street & Van Brunt Street, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Sackett Street - Van Brunt Street
text:
(1) 63-75 Sackett Street (right), east of the N.E. corner of Van Brunt Street. Also shown, is Van Brunt Street, east side, north of Sackett to Degraw Streets. March 27, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) The same, further eastward across clearing, showing a more extensive view. March 27, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.
